{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act15side_level_act15side_05_beg","storyGroup":"act15side","storySort":11,"storyDependence":"act15side_level_act15side_st02","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"IW-5","storyName":"货与人","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"郑掌柜先一步截下了名为夜半的窃贼，却被挑山人尚冢横插一脚，夺走酒盏。克洛丝一行也找到老船夫，打算与老鲤会合。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act15side/level_act15side_05_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act15side_05","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":9,"next":11,"characters":["郑掌柜","夜半","挑山人","克洛丝","老船夫","左乐","太合"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"5上","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.4","id":5,"musicid":0},{"type":"Background","image":"25_g05_mountaincity_d","screenadapt":"coverall","id":6},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"Text","text":"山上的风，总是清爽的。","id":8},{"type":"Text","text":"一个清爽的早晨，总是适合解决一些不清不楚的事情。","id":9},{"type":"Text","text":"山间小镇刚起炊烟，春雪未散，一老一小，相顾无言。","id":10},{"type":"Text","text":"只听远方一声击锣。","id":11},{"type":"dialog","id":12},{"type":"character","id":13},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":14},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"等你很久了。","id":16,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":17},{"type":"character","id":18},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#8$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":19},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":20},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......嘁，这家伙......阿灯，先不要轻举妄动。","id":21,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"我见过你，嗯，原来是你。","id":23,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"的确是出人意料，一个雷姆必拓人，一个从一开始就悄悄蛰伏在尚蜀的人。","id":24,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"我可听不懂啊。","id":26,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......哼。","id":28,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#11$1","id":29},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"阿灯！","id":30,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#11$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":31},{"type":"character","id":32},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":33},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"什——！？","id":35,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"套索？","id":37,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你把这些眠兽训练得不错，如果是寻常人，此刻就该倒栽葱扎在地里了。","id":38,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#8$1","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"（不仅能立刻发现背后的陷阱，还能稳稳把绳索踩在脚下......这老头......）","id":40,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"别担心，我不难为你一个姑娘家。","id":42,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你知道你怀里的那只酒盏，是什么东西吗？","id":43,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#11$1","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......我不关心，也不在乎。问太多的赏金猎人，都是新手。","id":45,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"那就要怪你自己了。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":48},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1","id":49},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":50},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"别这么得意！小帽！钻头！","id":51,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":52},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$normal02_intro","key":"$normal02_loop","volume":"0.4","id":53,"musicid":1},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":54},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","text":"","id":55},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.4","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":56},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","text":"","id":57},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":58},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_punch","text":"","id":59},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":60},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1","id":61},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"——","id":63,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":64},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"既然不知道是什么，就老老实实把东西交出来，不要白白遭人利用。","id":65,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1","id":66},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"你、你竟然对小帽——！你自找的！","id":67,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":68},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":69},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":70},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_atk_arrow_h","id":71},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":73},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":74},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......无头箭。","id":75,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1","id":76},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":77},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"（用、用手抓住了？这个距离！？我可是才给弩换过弦的——！）","id":78,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"好。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"念在你不愿意伤人性命的份上，我给你一个机会。","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"把这酒盏给我，然后告诉你背后的人：慎行，忌私。","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#8$1","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"哼，你知道我背后是谁？","id":84,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"知不知道不重要，重要的是，我能在这条路上堵住你。","id":86,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#8$1","id":87},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......我凭什么听你的？","id":88,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你没得选。","id":90,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你自己也许逃得掉，但你总不忍心看见，自己饲养的这些小畜生遭了殃。","id":91,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#8$1","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"你威胁我？","id":93,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你有些身手，可除了摆弄弓弩，也没啥功夫。","id":95,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"大可不必敬酒不吃吃罚酒，混江湖，是要靠眼力识人的。","id":96,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......确实，那个人也没和我说，会有你这样的高手来碍事。","id":98,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"如果我拜托一个人去做一件危险的事，那我也多半不会全盘托出的。","id":100,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"外乡人，一份工作而已，何必搭上身家性命？","id":101,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"把盏给我，我以镖局的名义担保，那人许你多少钱财，我们双倍奉上。","id":102,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#2$1","id":103},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......哈，本来就是亏本买卖，义务劳动。","id":104,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1","id":105},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"算是帮朋友忙吧。","id":106,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"朋友。","id":108,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"原来你这样的荒野流寇，也愿意为朋友两肋插刀。","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#11$1","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"你好像对我们有点意见。","id":111,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......没有的事。","id":113,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"生意做久了，贵人多了，朋友也就少了。","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#11$1","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"那你就老老实实回去做生意。","id":116,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#11$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"是啊，山上的生意是最好做的。","id":118,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"这三山十七峰几百条山道，哪条道上没有供人歇脚休憩的茶馆驿站，哪条道上......没有我们的人？","id":119,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......","id":121,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":122},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"望姑娘知晓轻重。","id":123,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"你还真不把我放在眼里。","id":125,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"虽然正面开战不是我的风格，但是都被挑衅到这个份上了......对吧，小家伙们。","id":126,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"（雷姆必拓语）让这个老家伙知道厉害！我们摸爬滚打这么多年，也不是吃干饭的！","id":128,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"唉......","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"执迷不悟。","id":131,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"若是如此，那就得罪——","id":133,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":134},{"type":"dialog","id":135},{"type":"character","id":136},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":137},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$swordtsing2","volume":"0.6","id":138},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"false","id":139},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":140},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":141},{"type":"Text","text":"哪怕有第三个人站在一旁，他也绝对看不清这一步，是怎么踏上前来的。","id":142},{"type":"Text","text":"只因为这个人擅长走路，擅长爬山。他每天抬步踏步的次数，实在是太多太多。","id":143},{"type":"Text","text":"一声脆响，地上，青砖碎裂，身前，烟尘蒙蒙，眼旁，是一根朴素无奇的竹木扁担，微微发青。","id":144},{"type":"Text","text":"远方，又一声击锣。","id":145},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......","id":147,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1","id":148},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"——怎、怎么......这个人是从哪里......啊，阿灯，别怕，钻头！快到我这里......！","id":150,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......是你。","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":153},{"type":"character","id":154},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":156},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":157},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.4","id":158,"musicid":2},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"你终于上山了。","id":159,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"所以我来找你。","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......唉。","id":162,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"该来的总要来。躲是躲不完的。你又何必这么着急？","id":163,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"喂，小女娃。","id":165,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......叫我？","id":167,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"（他的动作——这根木条是叫扁担来着？他刚才做了什么......把石砖地拍得粉碎？）","id":168,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"你认得他？","id":170,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"不。","id":172,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"那就是你们之间有什么麻烦。","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"我们之间只站着你。","id":176,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"说的对，那我就是你的麻烦。","id":178,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"事办完了，我会去找你。但不是现在。","id":180,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"......小女娃，和你手里护着的玩意，有关系？","id":182,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......啊......是......","id":184,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":185},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你我私仇，别扯上这件大事！","id":186,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":187},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"多大的事？","id":188,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"百姓安危，士卒存亡！","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......！","id":192,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#6$1","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"......自从那年雨夜之后，我很少听你有这样的语气了。","id":194,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#2$1","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"是啊。你怎么会是个恶人呢。一个侠义心肠的刀客，一个本分做人的掌柜。","id":196,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"那你就让开——","id":198,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"——可我正知道你是这样一个人，所以你不来见我。","id":200,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"你不见我，我去找你，也没有结果。所以我也没有下过山。","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"那如果......","id":202,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":203},{"type":"character","id":204},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_punch","volume":"0.6","id":205},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":206},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":207},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......啊！你——！","id":209,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"......","id":211,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"还给我！","id":213,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"......","id":215,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"......","id":216,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"......十年了。","id":217,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"十年前，你就是为了护这只酒盏......看着我儿子死于非命。","id":218,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......尚冢！","id":220,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"小女娃，这没你什么事了。","id":222,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1","id":223},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"你趁我不注意抢了我的货，还敢说没我事了！？","id":224,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"这货本来也不是你的。","id":226,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1","id":227},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"唔......","id":228,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":229},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"尚冢，你昏头了吗！","id":230,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"没你什么事了。","id":232,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"尚冢！","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#3$1","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"滚！","id":236,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#3$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"......嘁！","id":238,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"夜半","text":"你们最好记住......我一定会把东西抢回来！","id":239,"figure":"avg_476_blkngt_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":240},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":241},{"type":"move","name":"middle","xpos":"300","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":242},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0.5","id":243},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":244},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"......郑清钺。你的刀呢？","id":246,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"在家里。","id":248,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"哦。在家里。","id":250,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"那年雨夜，走镖路上，共牺牲了十几号人。其中有一个儿子，一个父亲。","id":251,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"儿子姓尚，是我的儿子。父亲姓杜，是杜遥夜的亲爹。","id":252,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"所以你就不戴刀了。","id":253,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"天大的笑话。","id":254,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......你恨我到现在。","id":256,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#6$1","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"我不恨你，我知道你不是故意的，责任在你，错不在你。","id":258,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"“先救货，再救人”，哼？","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"可货没了，人也没了，难道还不许我怨你？","id":261,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"我必须向你讨个说法，否则我活不下去。","id":262,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","id":263},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......我答应你。酒盏给我。你知道，这只酒盏牵扯——","id":264,"figure":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":265},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"我不知道。当年他为这只酒盏而死，今天，我要拿这只酒盏给他陪葬。","id":266,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"我在山上等你，等你去取刀。","id":267,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1.5","id":268},{"type":"dialog","id":269},{"type":"character","id":270},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":272},{"type":"Background","image":"25_g01_yanstreet_d","screenadapt":"coverall","id":273},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2.5","block":"true","id":274},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"$darkness02_loop","volume":"0.4","id":275,"musicid":3},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#4$1","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"......慎师傅！","id":277,"figure":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#4$1","name2":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"嗯？你们怎么先来了？我刚打算去梁府找你们哪。","id":279,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#4$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"鲤小子呢？","id":280,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#4$1","name2":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"那只酒盏被偷了，鲤先生让我们来找您来着。","id":282,"figure":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"他有交代过什么吗？","id":283,"figure":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#6$1","name2":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"......他让你们来找我，却没让你们先去找那梁大人？","id":285,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"你们分明是从梁府出来的？","id":286,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#6$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#6$1","name2":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":287},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"呃......是的。","id":288,"figure":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#5$1","name2":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"......唉。没让你们找梁洵，说明他心底里已经知道了......","id":290,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#2$1","name2":"avg_1021_kroos2_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":291},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"人精，人精，确实是人精。","id":292,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#2$1"},{"type":"dialog","id":293},{"type":"character","id":294},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":295},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":296},{"type":"Background","image":"25_g04_yaninn","screenadapt":"coverall","id":297},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":298},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":299},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":300},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":301},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":302},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"太合叔，回来了？","id":303,"figure":"avg_npc_297_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"如何？","id":305,"figure":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太合","text":"以她身份而言，礼数周到，名副其实。","id":307,"figure":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"愿意演这番礼数周到，说明还有斡旋余地。","id":309,"figure":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"不论她本人做何动作，有何居心。太傅手谕在此，作不得假。","id":310,"figure":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太合","text":"她是个聪明人。","id":312,"figure":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太合","text":"我既以官身拜访，她当有所觉察。","id":313,"figure":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......好。","id":315,"figure":"avg_npc_297_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_299_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":316},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太合","text":"如今两方都如劲弓满弦，一触即发。","id":317,"figure":"avg_npc_299_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":318},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太合","text":"唯有在惹出更多口舌非议之前，了结事端。","id":319,"figure":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":320},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"如果真的要让所有人相信，我们的选择能让大炎永除后患，那我们自然得依那四个字——","id":321,"figure":"avg_npc_297_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":322},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"——光明磊落。","id":323,"figure":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":324},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"Character","id":326},{"type":"Image","id":327}],"characters":["郑掌柜","夜半","挑山人","克洛丝","老船夫","左乐","太合"]}